title: Astros Implode To Let Royals Back Into ALDS
text:
> Sports Astros Implode To Let Royals Back Into ALDS Astros shortstop Carlos Correa couldn’t handle a deflected grounder that might have been a double-play ball, helping the Kansas City Royals rally for five runs in the eighth inning to beat Houston 9-6 The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
